# Twilio Hosted Numbers Setup Script

## Overview
This script is designed to automate the setup process for Twilio Hosted Numbers. It utilizes the Twilio API to create orders for bulk hosted numbers based on predefined configurations.

## Requirements
- Node.js installed on your system.
- Twilio Account SID and Auth Token.
- Environment variables set in a `.env` file (see `.env.example` for reference).

